headline: Dow Inc.: Buy, Sell, or Hold?
summary: The big draw for investors with Dow Inc. (NYSE: DOW) is its huge 7.8% dividend yield.  While that will clearly be attractive to income investors, it has to be juxtaposed against the company's business risks.  There are reasons some investors might want to buy or hold Dow, but selling (or avoiding) it is also an equally worthy choice.
